OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FHundreds of soldiers and firefighters
OL,7,Fhave been deployed to fight the blaze
OL,9,FFour Brits are feared to be among 12
OL,10,Fpeople killed by wildfires in southern
OL,11,FSpain as soaring temperatures gripped
OL,12,Fmuch of the country, local authorities
OL,13,Fsaid on Friday.
OL,15,FSeveral victims of the fire in Almeria
OL,16,Fwere found inside burned-out vehicles,
OL,17,Flocal media reported.
OL,19,FEight people have been injured in the
OL,20,Fblaze and 23 were missing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
