OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783712872
OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FAntonio Sanz, Andalusia's health and
OL,7,Femergencies minister, said the people
OL,8,Finside one of the cars were believed
OL,9,Fto be "of British origin".
OL,11,FHe said the vehicle they were found in
OL,12,Fhad the steering wheel on the right.
OL,14,FBodies were found near the village of
OL,15,FBedar, in Almeria province.
OL,17,FAuthorities believe the other seven
OL,18,Fvictims were also foreign tourists.
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@YO]
