OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FThey were thought to have attempted to
OL,7,Fescape on foot after apparently
OL,8,Fabandoning their vehicles and trying
OL,9,Fto flee through rugged terrain.
OL,11,F"The decision to take another route
OL,12,Finstead of the designated evacuation
OL,13,Froute became a fatal trap," Mr Sanz
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FHe said the victims had sought "their
OL,17,Fown way out" through a dry riverbed
OL,18,Frather than following the route
OL,19,Fcoordinated by emergency services.
