OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FThe fire broke out in a hamlet in a
OL,7,Fsemi-arid area near the Sierra de Los
OL,8,FFilabres mountains. Authorities have
OL,9,Fnot confirmed the cause of the fire,
OL,10,Fbut said people who called to report
OL,11,Fit said that a fallen power line had
OL,12,Fsparked a blaze that spread rapidly
OL,13,Finto a nearby forest.
OL,15,FSpain's military emergency unit, which
OL,16,Fis deployed in major emergencies, was
OL,17,Fdue to join firefighting efforts in
OL,18,Fthe coming hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
