PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783712872
OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FThe fire also led to road closures,
OL,7,Fwhile 1,000 residents were evacuated,
OL,8,Faccording to emergency services.
OL,10,FRegional authorities said the fire was
OL,11,Fthe deadliest in the region to date.
OL,13,FJuan Manuel Moreno, the regional
OL,14,Fleader of the southern Andalusia
OL,15,Fregion, wrote on X that "Our hearts
OL,16,Fare heavy and we are devastated by
OL,17,Fgrief."
