OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FSpanish Prime Minister Pedro Sanchez
OL,7,Fexpressed his condolences, writing on
OL,8,FX of his "immense sadness and
OL,9,Fdesolation in the face of the terrible
OL,10,Fconsequences of the fire affecting the
OL,11,Fprovince of Almeria."
OL,13,FSpain has battled frequent and severe
OL,14,Fheatwaves in recent years, with
OL,15,Ftemperatures often exceeding 40C.
OL,16,FWind, high temperatures and little
OL,17,Frainfall help small wildfires grow
OL,18,Finto unchecked blazes.
