OL,3,CFour Brits feared to be among 12
OL,4,Cpeople killed in huge Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FIn June, Spain experienced several
OL,7,Fdays of record-setting heat, with more
OL,8,Fthan 1,000 excess deaths attributed to
OL,9,Fheat.
